"""Tests for the init of asy_fit"""
st = cs.st
asymptotic_fit(st, norders=cs.pars['norders'])

    'likelihood', 'model', 'norders', 'par_names', 'pg', 'plot_corner',
    'plot_echelle', 'plot_prior', 'plot_spectrum', 'plot_start', 'prior',
    'prior_file', 's', 'sel', 'start', 'start_samples', '_P_envelope']
pbt.assert_hasattributes(st.asy_fit, attributes)
